      <tr><td>Oven light + installation</td><td>$115 – $175</td><td>Premium high-temp bulb</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="small">Miele service runs 30-50% above mainstream-brand equivalent reflecting premium parts pricing + Miele-specific factory-credentialed diagnostic depth. Legacy H 5000 units may add 10-15 day parts-lead for specialty components from Princeton NJ.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap">
